Paper: hep-th/0005060

Date: 2000-05-07

Title: Difficulties in a Kind of Averaging Procedure for Constructing

Gauge-invariant Operators out of Gauge-variant OnesAuthors: Wei-Min Sun, Xiang-Song Chen and Fan Wang

Comments: 3 pages, revtex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B483 (2000) 299-302

We prove that a kind of averaging procedure for constructing gauge-invariantoperators(or functionals) out of gauge-variant ones is erroneous andinapplicable for a large class of operators(or functionals).